Class Namespace

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.fhir.model.api.BaseElement

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompositeElement, IElement, IResource, ISupportsUndeclaredExtensions

    public class Namespace
extends BaseResource
implements IResource
    HAPI/FHIR Namespace Resource (System of unique identification)

    Definition: A curated namespace that issues unique symbols within that namespace for the identification of concepts, people, devices, etc. Represents a \"System\" used within the Identifier and Coding data types.

    Requirements:

    Profile Definition: http://hl7.org/fhir/profiles/Namespace
